WEBVTT

00:04:58.360 --> 00:05:01.760
Diplomacy had failed to stop the Germans.

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:05.752
Only brute force remained.

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:08.320
It was our last resort.

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:12.720
My father was there to provide it.

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:17.856
As the son of a farmer
who knew how to hunt,

00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:20.120
my father was an excellent marksman.

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:23.560
When he aimed, he never missed.

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:27.816
At this decisive moment in Dutch history

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:32.656
my father was positioned
on the bank of the river Waal